      "date": "2015-10-02 21:23:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\n(2 comments)\n\nI'm not against this patch, but it would be good to have a test case to verify what actually causing this problem and whether this patch is fixing it.\n\nIt seems that what is needed is a fail_loc that will trigger the ENOSPC/EDQUOT handling like OBD_FAIL_OSC_NO_GRANT together with fsx so that it can do partial-page writes that might be merged.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
