      "date": "2015-11-24 18:54:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nWhile I would have liked a regression test for this bug, I'm happy that it at least fixed the problem in Cray's regression tests and we can hope they will continue to run those tests in the future.\n\nI'm OK with landing this as-is, but it needs another review.",
